div.p: The Campbell R-II School District is now accepting applications for 2 teacher’s aide positions. Applicants must have 60 hours of college credit or pass the Paraprofessional test in the State of Missouri. The successful applicants will work with early childhood and special needs students. If interested, please complete the district application found at www.campbell.k12.mo.us or pick an application up in the central office. Please include resume, transcripts, and references. For questions regarding the position please contact Ben Foster at bfoster@campbell.k12.mo.us or 573-246-3109 or Jay Thornton at jay@campbell.k12.mo.us or 573-246-2133 ext. 4.

div.p: The Campbell R-II School District will be closed beginning Wednesday, March 18th through the end of the school year. All school activities will be cancelled during this time. Please see our district Facebook page for more detailed information and for ongoing announcements.
